<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" ?>
<group>
    <text>
        <title>HyperOS/MIUI</title>
        <desc>提供适用于Magisk或KernelSU的模块，提供mtz主题包（需要主题破解）</desc>
    </text>
</group>
<group>
  <text>
    <title>配置</title>
  </text>
        <picker auto-off="true" interruptible="false" shell="hidden" icon="pic/style.png">
            <title>选择主题图标</title>
            <options>
                <option value="default">MIUI经典(推荐)</option>
                <option value="explore">MIUI探·界(推荐)</option>
                <option value="Hyper">HyperOS(需HyperOS桌面)</option>
                <option value="coloros13">ColorOS13(推荐)</option>
                <option value="coloros12">ColorOS12(推荐)</option>
                <option value="flyme9">Flyme9(推荐)</option>
                <option value="flyme10">Flyme10(Beta)</option>
                <option value="iOS">iOS</option>
                <option value="lrone">Lrone</option>
                <option value="luck7">Luck7</option>
                <option value="perfectcurve">完美曲线</option>
                <option value="Aquamarine">鸿蒙-润泽</option>
                <option value="AmethystLake">EMUI-紫晶湖</option>
                <option value="GoldenBeach">EMUI-碧海金沙</option>
                <option value="LightWings">EMUI-光之翼</option>
                <option value="Nebulae">EMUI-宇宙之眼</option>
                <option value="StarrySky">EMUI-星夜彩绘</option>
                <option value="Reconstruction">EMUI-未来之翼</option>
            </options>
            <auto-off>true</auto-off>
            <summary sh="source online-scripts/misc/get_seltheme_name.sh" />
            <get> 
            source theme_files/theme_config
            echo $sel_theme 
            </get>
            <set>echo "sel_theme=$state" &gt; theme_files/theme_config </set>
        </picker>
    <page icon="pic/addon.png" before-read="source online-scripts/misc/addon_init.sh">
        <config>addon.xml</config>
        <title>图标自定义</title>
        <desc>图标自定义的开关、配置说明及图标存档下载</desc>
    </page>
    <page icon="pic/disabledynamic.png">
        <config>disabledynamicicons.xml</config>
        <title>禁用动态图标</title>
        <desc>可禁用某些或全部图标的动画效果</desc>
    </page>
    <switch shell="hidden" icon="pic/addon.png">
        <title>是否启用新版遮罩</title>
        <desc>如果你使用的是HyperOS的新桌面，请开启这个选项。如果是MIUI那就关闭。如果图标大小异常，可尝试切换。</desc>
        <get>
            source theme_files/new_transform_config
            echo $new_transform_config
        </get>
        <set>echo "new_transform_config=$state" &gt; theme_files/new_transform_config</set>
    </switch>
</group>

<group visible="source online-scripts/misc/installer_check.sh">
  <text visible="source online-scripts/misc/installer_check.sh notboth">
    <title>安装模块</title>
  </text>
  <text visible="source online-scripts/misc/installer_check.sh both">
      <title>安装模块</title>
      <desc>注意：如果您同时将模块安装到Magisk和KernelSU，请自行处理二者优先级关系。建议模块仅应用在一种root方案中。</desc>
  </text>
        <action confirm="true" icon="pic/magisk.png" reload="@install,@cleancache" before-read="source online-scripts/misc/addon_init.sh" visible="source online-scripts/misc/installer_check.sh magisk">
            <title>安装模块（Magisk）</title>
            <desc>确认上述配置无误后，将以 Magisk 模块方式安装完美图标。</desc>
            <summary sh="source online-scripts/misc/get_themes.sh magisk" />
            <set>source $START_DIR/online-scripts/misc/module.sh magisk</set>
        </action>

        <action confirm="true" icon="pic/kernelsu.png" reload="@install,@cleancache" before-read="source online-scripts/misc/addon_init.sh" visible="source online-scripts/misc/installer_check.sh kernelsu">
            <title>安装模块（KernelSU）</title>
            <desc>确认上述配置无误后，将以 KernelSU 模块方式安装完美图标。</desc>
            <summary sh="source online-scripts/misc/get_themes.sh kernelsu" />
            <set>source $START_DIR/online-scripts/misc/module.sh kernelsu</set>
        </action>

        <action confirm="true" icon="pic/reboot.png" shell="hidden" warning="确认重启？">
            <title>重启设备</title>
            <desc>轻触重启</desc>
            <set>/system/bin/sync;/system/bin/svc power reboot || reboot</set>
        </action>
</group>

<group>
  <text>
    <title>下载至本地</title>
  </text>
    <action shell="hidden" icon="pic/folder.png">
        <title>选择文件保存位置</title>
        <param name="dir" type="folder" value="/sdcard/Download" />
        <summary sh="source theme_files/zipoutdir_config ; echo 当前路径为：$zipoutdir " />
        <set>echo "zipoutdir=$dir" &gt; theme_files/zipoutdir_config</set>
    </action>
    <action icon="pic/save.png" reload="@cleancache">
        <title>下载模块包</title>
        <desc>确认上述配置无误后，下载模块后可自行进行安装</desc>
        <set>source $START_DIR/online-scripts/misc/module.sh save</set>
    </action>
    <action icon="pic/save.png" reload="@cleancache">
        <title>下载mtz主题包</title>
        <desc>确认上述配置无误后，下载mtz主题包，需要主题破解才能应用。</desc>
        <set>source $START_DIR/online-scripts/misc/module.sh mtz</set>
    </action>
</group>

<group>
  <text>
    <title>其他</title>
  </text>
         <page title="预览主题图标" html="https://icons-demo.pedroz.eu.org/" icon="pic/preview.png"/>
         <page config="page/install.xml" title="使用说明及常见问题" icon="pic/qa.png"/>
</group>

